  "texts": [
    "Software-based training was performed using a 32 × 30 sub-array of the 1 kb CA.",
    "To match the dimensions of the CA network, the MNIST images were resized from 28 × 28 pixels to 20 × 16 pixels.",
    "During the training process, the resized MNIST data was reshaped into a 320 × 1 matrix.",
    "Since the CA density was insufficient to accommodate 320 inputs, we divided the 32 × 30 matrix into ten sets of 32 × 3 matrices.",
    "Therefore, the reshaped 320 × 1 images were partitioned into 10 sets of 32 × 1 as shown in Fig. 3a."
  ],
